title: Enable Flakes in Home-Manager
tags: @zettel _method nix homemanager
roam-id: bff70461-690e-4cb2-aec3-3c8c4b82e33b
type: text/markdown

in your `~/.config/home-manager/home.nix` put the following\`

``` nix
{
  ...
  nix = {
    package = pkgs.nix;
    settings.experimental-features = [ "nix-command" "flakes" ];
  };
  ...
}
```
